{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3329-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1941"},"text":"§ 1941.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Persons eligible for loans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Eligibility requirements","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may make and insure loans under this subchapter to farmers and ranchers in the United States, and to farm cooperatives and private domestic corporations, partnerships, joint operations, trusts, limited liability companies, and such other legal entities as the Secretary considers appropriate, that are controlled by farmers and ranchers and engaged primarily and directly in farming or ranching in the United States, subject to the conditions specified in this section. To be eligible for such loans, applicants who are individuals, or, in the case of cooperatives, corporations, partnerships, joint operations, trusts, limited liability companies, and such other legal entities, individuals holding a majority interest in such entity, must (A) be citizens of the United States, (B) for direct loans only, have either training or farming experience that the Secretary determines is sufficient to assure reasonable prospects of success in the proposed farming operations, taking into consideration all farming experience of the applicant, without regard to any lapse between farming experiences, (C) be or will become operators of not larger than family farms (or in the case of cooperatives, corporations, partnerships, joint operations, trusts, limited liability companies, and such other legal entities in which a majority interest is held by individuals who are related by blood or marriage, as defined by the Secretary, such individuals must be or will become either owners or operators of not larger than a family farm and at least one such individual must be or will become an operator of not larger than a family farm or, in the case of holders of the entire interest who are related by blood or marriage and all of whom are or will become farm operators, the ownership interest of each such holder separately constitutes not larger than a family farm, even if their interests collectively constitute larger than a family farm, as defined by the Secretary), and (D) be unable to obtain sufficient credit elsewhere to finance their actual needs at reasonable rates and terms, taking into consideration prevailing private and cooperative rates and terms in the community in or near which the applicant resides for loans for similar purposes and periods of time. In addition to the foregoing requirements of this subsection, in the case of corporations, partnerships, joint operations, trusts, limited liability companies, and such other legal entities, the family farm requirement of subparagraph (C) of the preceding sentence shall apply as well to the farm or farms in which the entity has an operator interest and the requirement of subparagraph (D) of the preceding sentence shall apply as well to the entity in the case of cooperatives, corporations, partnerships, joint operations, trusts, limited liability companies, and such other legal entities.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Special rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"An entity that is an operator described in paragraph (1) that is owned, in whole or in part, by other entities, shall be considered to meet the direct ownership requirement imposed under paragraph (1) if at least 75 percent of the ownership interests of each embedded entity of the entity is owned directly or indirectly by the individuals that own the family farm.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Rural youths in 4–H Clubs, Future Farmers of America, etc.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Loans may also be made under this subchapter without regard to the requirements of clauses (2) and (3) of subsection (a) to youths to enable them to operate enterprises in connection with their participation in 4–H Clubs, Future Farmers of America, and similar organizations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f332f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A person receiving a loan under this subsection who executes a promissory note therefor shall thereby incur full personal liability for the indebtedness evidenced by such note in accordance with its terms free of any disability of minority.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3330-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For loans under this subsection the Secretary may accept the personal liability of a cosigner of the promissory note in addition to the borrowers’ personal liability.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3331-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Youth enterprises not farming or ranching","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The operation of an enterprise by a youth under this subsection shall not be considered the operation of a farm or ranch under this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3332-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Equitable considerations for default.—","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3333-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/5/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Debt forgiveness.—","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3334-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/5/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In general","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may, on a case-by-case basis, provide debt forgiveness to a borrower for a loan made under this subsection if the borrower was unable to timely repay the loan due to circumstances beyond the control of the borrower, as determined by the Secretary, including any natural disaster, act of terrorism, or other man-made disaster that results in an inordinate level of damage or disruption severely affecting the borrower.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3335-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/5/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Eligibility for future loans","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of law, debt forgiveness provided under this subparagraph shall not be used by any Federal agency in determining the eligibility of the borrower for any loan made or guaranteed by the agency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3336-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/b/5/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Education loans","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of law, if a borrower becomes delinquent or is provided with debt forgiveness with respect to a youth loan made under this subsection, the borrower shall not become ineligible, as a result of the delinquency or debt forgiveness, to receive loans and loan guarantees from the Federal Government to pay for education expenses of the borrower.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3337-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Direct loans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3338-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Subject to paragraphs (3) and (4), the Secretary may make a direct loan under this subchapter only to a farmer or rancher who—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3339-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is a qualified beginning farmer or rancher;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" has not received a previous direct operating loan made under this subchapter; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" has received a previous direct operating loan made under this subchapter during 6 or fewer years.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definition of direct operating loan","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this subsection, the term “direct operating loan” does not include—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a loan made to a youth under subsection (b); or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a microloan made to a beginning farmer or rancher or a veteran farmer or rancher (as defined in section 2279(e) ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002215"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002215"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f333f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transition rule","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If, as of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-04-04"},"text":"April 4, 1996","children":[],"tail":", a farmer or rancher has received a direct operating loan under this subchapter during each of 4 or more previous years, the borrower shall be eligible to receive a direct operating loan under this subchapter during 3 additional years after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-04-04"},"text":"April 4, 1996","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3340-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Waivers","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3341-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Farm and ranch operations on tribal lands","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall waive the limitation under paragraph (1)(C) or (3) for a direct loan made under this subchapter to a farmer or rancher whose farm or ranch land is subject to the jurisdiction of an Indian tribe and whose loan is secured by 1 or more security instruments that are subject to the jurisdiction of an Indian tribe if the Secretary determines that commercial credit is not generally available for such farm or ranch operations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef0f3342-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Other farm and ranch operations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"On a case-by-case determination not subject to administrative appeal, the Secretary may grant a borrower a waiver, 1 time only for a period of 2 years, of the limitation under paragraph (1)(C) or (3) for a direct operating loan if the borrower demonstrates to the satisfaction of the Secretary that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c33-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the borrower has a viable farm or ranch operation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c34-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the borrower applied for commercial credit from at least 2 commercial lenders;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c35-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/B/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the borrower was unable to obtain a commercial loan (including a loan guaranteed by the Secretary); and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c36-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/4/B/iv"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iv"},"text":"(iv)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the borrower successfully has completed, or will complete within 1 year, borrower training under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2006a"},"text":"section 2006a of this title","children":[],"tail":" (from which requirement the Secretary shall not grant a waiver under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2006a/f"},"text":"section 2006a(f) of this title","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef117c37-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual report on term limits on direct operating loans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef117c38-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall prepare a report annually that describes—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c39-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the status of the direct operating loan program of the Department of Agriculture; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the impact of term limits on direct loan borrowers.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Demographic information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The report shall provide a demographic breakdown, on a State-by-State basis, of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/B/i/I"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"I"},"text":"(I)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" all direct loan borrowers; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/B/i/II"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"II"},"text":"(II)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" borrowers that have reached the eligibility limit for direct lending programs during the previous calendar year.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c3f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Demographic information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The available demographic information shall include, to the maximum extent practicable, a description of race or ethnicity, gender, age, type of farm or ranch, financial classification, number of years of indebtedness, veteran status, and other similar information, as determined by the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef117c40-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional content","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In addition to information described in subparagraph (B), the report shall provide—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c41-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/C/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a demographic analysis of the borrowers impacted by term limits;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c42-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/C/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" information on the conditions impacting the direct lending portfolio of the Department of Agriculture, including impacts by region and agriculture sector, and credit availability within those regions and sectors;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c43-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/C/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to the maximum extent practicable, information on the status of borrower operations impacted by term limits; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c44-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/C/iv"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iv"},"text":"(iv)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" recommendations, if appropriate, to address any identifiable unmet credit needs.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef117c45-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Submission","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c46-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/D/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" annually submit to the Committee on Agriculture of the House of Representatives and the Committee on Agriculture, Nutrition, and Forestry of the Senate a copy of the report; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idef117c47-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1941/c/5/D/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" make the report available to the public, including posting the report on the website of the Department of Agriculture.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef117c48-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128/tIII/s311"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128, title III, § 311","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/310"},"text":"75 Stat. 310","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":